{{Han char|rn=115|rad=禾|as=08|sn=13|canj=HDKLU|four=|ids=⿰禾奄}}

# (same as [[馣]]) sweet-smelling
# tasty, delicious
# to farm, to cultivate the land
# luxuriant or exuberant of growing rice
# grains,, rice plants producing no fruit
# to fertilize
# the grains not growing, shriveled rice plants
